mething that is so important that it is likely to be remembered:<ul class=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\" hclass=\"examples\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Today is a historic occasion for our country.</span></li></ul></li><li class=\"li\"><span class=\"eb\">Historical</span> usually describes something that is connected with the past or with the study of history, or something that really happened in the past:<ul class=\"examples\" hclass=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">I have been doing some historical research.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Was Robin Hood a historical figure?</span></li></ul></li></ul></span></span></div><span class=\"topic-g\"><span class=\"prefix\">Topics </span><a class=\"Ref\" href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/topic/history?level=b1\" title=\"Topic history\"><span class=\"topic\" href=\"l2:time_and_space:history?cefr=b1\"><span class=\"topic_name\">History</span><span class=\"topic_cefr\">b1</span></span></a></span>          \n</li><li class=\"sense\" sensenum=\"2\" hclass=\"sense\" cefr=\"b1\" id=\"historic_sng_2\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"sensetop\" hclass=\"sensetop\" htag=\"span\"><span class=\"def\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"def\">of a period during which history was recorded</span></span><ul class=\"examples\" hclass=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">in historic times</span></li></ul> <span class=\"xrefs\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"xrefs\" xt=\"cp\"><span class=\"prefix\">compare</span> <a class=\"Ref\" href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/prehistoric\" title=\"prehistoric definition\"><span class=\"xr-g\" href=\"prehistoric_e\" bord=\"n\"><span class=\"xh\">prehistoric</span></span></a></span><span class=\"topic-g\"><span class=\"prefix\">Topics </span><a class=\"Ref\" href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/topic/history?level=b1\" title=\"Topic history\"><span class=\"to